<title>NIGERIA: Nigerian Hoechst posts improved '96 profit.</title>
<headline>Nigerian Hoechst posts improved '96 profit.</headline>
<dateline>LAGOS 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Full year result for Nigerian-German Chemicals Company (NGCC), formerly Nigerian Hoechst to end-December 1996.</p>
<p>(In million naira unless stated)</p>
<p>					1996	    1995</p>
<p>     Turnover		    928.9	    718.5</p>
<p>     Profit before taxation    131	    120.8</p>
<p>     Taxation			 28	     22.2</p>
<p>     Profit after taxation   102.9	     98.5</p>
<p>     Proposed dividend 50 kobo per share   50 kobo</p>
<p>Note: The company changed to its present name about two years ago.</p>
<p>($1=85 naira)</p>
<p>-- Lagos newsroom +234 1 263 03 17</p>
